---
export const prerender = true;
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Claim a Listing</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Claim your business listing on ProNest New England and request verification."
    />

    <style>
      :root {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: #fff;
        color: #111;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 0 16px 56px;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        font-size: 34px;
        line-height: 1.1;
      }

      h2 {
        margin-top: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .intro {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #444;
        max-width: 680px;
      }

      ol,
      ul {
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding-left: 22px;
      }

      .claim-box {
        margin-top: 28px;
        padding: 16px 18px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: #fafafa;
      }

      .claim-box strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .claim-email {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #111827;
        text-decoration: none;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .claim-email:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .note {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }

      .back-link {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #111827;
      }

      .back-link:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Claim a Listing</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        If you own or manage a business listed on ProNest New England, you can
        claim your listing and request verification. Verified listings help
        customers identify trusted local businesses and ensure your business
        information is accurate.
      </p>

      <h2>How to claim</h2>

      <ol>
        <li>Email <strong>claims@pronestne.com</strong>.</li>

        <li>
          Include the following information:
          <ul>
            <li>Business name</li>
            <li>Town and service category</li>
            <li>Your name and role with the business</li>
            <li>Your phone number</li>
            <li>Link to your website or Google Business Profile</li>
          </ul>
        </li>

        <li>
          We will review the information and update your listing once verified.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <div class="claim-box">
        <strong>Claim email</strong>
        <a class="claim-email" href="mailto:claims@pronestne.com">
          claims@pronestne.com
        </a>

        <div class="note">
          Include your business details and verification information in your
          message.
        </div>
      </div>

      <a class="back-link" href="/">← Back to home</a>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>